Package oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.socialnetwork.ui.managed

Class Summary
SocialNetworkBackingBean Backing Bean to hold all of the binding information, etc for the Social Network Setup page.
SocialNetworkPageFlowBean The base clase for a node that can be inserted into the Social Network Setups page Objects tree-table.
SocialNetworkRangeModel Range model for the Social Network Sending to OSN popup.
SocialNetworkSendThread Thread to be used when sending information to OSN in the background.
SocialNetworkSessionBean Deprecated. Do not use this class, it will be removed in 11.1.1.8.0 timeframe.
SocialNetworkSetupSessionBean A container for information that needs to be kept in the session to support the Manage Oracle Social Network taskflow.
